        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down</placeName>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
                    <p>[…] Permit me to advise you to try not to be troubled about the differences between ecclesiastics &amp; scientific men.<ref target="#foot.f3"/> Search for the truth, &amp; then your conscience will be at ease. In the course of time ecclesiastics have always managed to make their conclusions somehow to harmonise with ascertained truths, which they at first vehemently &amp; ignorantly opposed […]</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
            
